 They looked at the key words and formulas in the news to uncover terrorist plans and cross-border crimes 

00:02:34.170 --> 00:02:37.885
 and every communication stream was passed to the intelligence analyst. 

00:02:38.417 --> 00:02:43.347
 This base was associated with the future of the US National Security Agency and GCHQ. 

00:02:43.510 --> 00:02:45.078
 And it's not the only place. 

